    <summary><span data-ttu-id="f163c-101">在 Web 客户端上以隐藏的 HTML 元素存储 ASP.NET 页面视图状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f163c-101">Stores ASP.NET page view state on the Web client in a hidden HTML element.</span></span></summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f163c-102">ASP.NET 页可以将 <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> 状态存储在本质上无状态 HTTP 请求和处理和服务任何网页所需的响应之间。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f163c-102">ASP.NET pages can store <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> state between the inherently stateless HTTP request and response required to process and serve any Web page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f163c-103">此状态称为 "视图状态"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f163c-103">This state is called "view state".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f163c-104">用于存储页及其控件的视图状态的默认机制位于从 Web 服务器提供给客户端的页中包含的一个或多个 `<hidden>` HTML 字段中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f163c-104">The default mechanism used to store view state for a page and its controls is in one or more `<hidden>` HTML fields included in the page that is served to a client from a Web server.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f163c-105"><xref:System.Web.UI.Page> 类可以使用 <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> 类来执行此操作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f163c-105">The <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> class can use the <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> class to do this work.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f163c-106"><xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> 实现 <xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister> 类的 <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Save%2A> 和 <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Load%2A> 方法，以便 <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> 可以将状态存储在 Web 客户端上名为 "`<hidden>`" 的 __VIEWSTATE HTML 元素中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f163c-106"><xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> implements the <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Save%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Load%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister> class so that the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> can store state in a `<hidden>` HTML element named "__VIEWSTATE" on a Web client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f163c-107">当客户端请求来自 Web 服务器（回发）的同一页面时，ASP.NET 将分析 `<hidden>` 元素，并将其转换为状态信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f163c-107">When the client requests the same page from the Web server (a postback), the `<hidden>` element is parsed and converted to state information by ASP.NET.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f163c-108">如果请求的 <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> 实例具有关联的 <xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter> 类，则它将使用 <xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A> 方法从此适配器检索 <xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister> 对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f163c-108">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> instance that is requested has an associated <xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter> class, it retrieves the <xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister> object from this adapter using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f163c-109">适配器可以重写 <xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A> 方法以返回按特定客户端支持的某种方式存储页和控件状态的 <xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister> 对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f163c-109">Adapters can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A> method to return a <xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister> object that stores page and control state in some way that a specific client supports.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f163c-110">例如，<xref:System.Web.UI.SessionPageStatePersister> 类将页面和控件的状态存储在 Web 服务器上，而不是客户端上，以减少必须在内存和带宽可能有限的客户端上发送和存储的信息量。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f163c-110">For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.SessionPageStatePersister> class stores page and controls' state on the Web server, instead of the client, to decrease the amount of information that must be sent and stored on a client that has potentially limited memory and bandwidth.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f163c-111">可以通过 <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A> 属性或通过 <xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A> 配置设置，设置 "_VIEWSTATE" `<hidden>` HTML 元素的最大大小。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f163c-111">The maximum size of the "_VIEWSTATE" `<hidden>` HTML element can be set through the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A> property or through the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A> configuration setting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f163c-112">如果设置了此值，并且 "_VIEWSTATE" 元素的长度超出了最大长度，则内容将被划分为多个 "_VIEWSTATE" 元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f163c-112">When this value is set and the length of the "_VIEWSTATE" element would exceed the maximum length, the content is divided into multiple "_VIEWSTATE" elements.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
